    "description": "点击绘图 是一款需要运用逻辑思维完成谜题，并在轻松愉快的氛围中绘制精美画作的解密游戏。化身画家，挥洒色彩，让你的作品成为挽救阿米美术馆的救世之作！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/f4fe16825fd61d3fdeb05d25a9351728.poster.avif?t=1762853114\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/f4fe16825fd61d3fdeb05d25a9351728.webm?t=1762853114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/f4fe16825fd61d3fdeb05d25a9351728.mp4?t=1762853114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/cf878db98e3f7cf62ed6e9b5ae3cbefd.poster.avif?t=1762853114\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/cf878db98e3f7cf62ed6e9b5ae3cbefd.webm?t=1762853114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>在 Click Painter 中，您可以使用高级扫雷规则解决谜题并完成绘画，无需任何猜测。每个格子里的数字代表着周围应该有多少相同颜色的颜料。根据这些数字提示，推理出每个格子应该填什么颜料，挥洒出正确的色彩吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/3ade910f241295cd70f4b28b468fb86a.poster.avif?t=1762853114\" width=600 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/3ade910f241295cd70f4b28b468fb86a.webm?t=1762853114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/3ade910f241295cd70f4b28b468fb86a.mp4?t=1762853114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在轻松舒缓的氛围中，按照自己的节奏解谜，你很快就能完成一幅色彩缤纷的画作。无论是可爱的小狗、威武的龙、动听的口琴、俏皮的雪人，还是神秘的魔法师，快来发挥你的创造力，绘制出丰富多彩的画卷吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/39862c3502f44c92f864c7cf11b27316.avif?t=1762853114\" width=592 height=300 /></span><br><br>您完成的图片越多，您可以获得的成就和有趣的动画就越多.<br>收集所有成就和动画！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/0c4aa0acc0ba75918677959e6f9cc3c9.avif?t=1762853114\" width=300 height=300 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/70676f621cbb7a4bef95a887dba7f0e1.gif?t=1762853114\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/70676f621cbb7a4bef95a887dba7f0e1.poster.avif?t=1762853114\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>高难度的新型解谜<br></li><li>轻松舒缓的氛围<br></li><li>有大約 100 個色彩缤纷的关卡<br></li><li>所有谜题都是可以解决的<br></li><li>各种成就和特殊动画<br></li><li>丰富有趣的随机关卡和自定义模式</li></ul>",
